DURBAN - Having had a glittering career both as a competitor and a trainer, Chris Bright, the BJJ Black Belt and undefeated Mixed Martial Artist joins The Clinch whilst overlooking the Indian Ocean on Durban's North Coast, to reminisce about the early days of the South African MMA scene and his journey through the years to his current tenure at PESFA (Port Elizabeth Submission Fighting Academy). Don't miss this fascinating insight into the fighting life of one of Africa's most revered combat athletes. eNCA